<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240);"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">购票方式：</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240);"><strong style="font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">1</span></strong><strong style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">、网上订票：</span></strong></span><br></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">台铁网络订票有95折优惠，大陆居民需要使用英文版页面订票，订票后，会给一个“电脑代码”。凭此信用卡付款和出票。最好打印出来。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><strong style="font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">订票时间：</span></strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">24小时运营</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><strong style="font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">订票张数：</span></strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">预约订票每人(身分证字号)每乘车日最多可预订6张乘车票，来回票可预订12张(去回程各6张)。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><strong style="font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">订票日期：</span></strong><strong style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 240); background: white;">乘车前十四天</span></strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">开始预订，乘车当日可预订开车前一小时以上之车票。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><strong style="font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">付款及取票期限：</span></strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">自订票日起2日内(含订票日)须完成取票或于付款网站完成付款。乘车当日订票后，须于开车前30分钟完成付款取票。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><strong style="font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">取票地点/手续费：</span></strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">在台北火车站可使用自助取票，无手续费；在高铁人工柜台取票，也不要手续费；在711/全家等等便利店取票，要手续8元人民币的手续费。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">台铁网上订票地址：</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><a href="/fishtrip/taiwan/taibei/" style="word-wrap: break-word;" target="_blank">http://www.tan90.cn/fishtrip/taiwan/taibei/</a></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240);"><strong style="font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">2</span></strong><strong style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">、台北火车站购票</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">台北到花莲的火车还是比较频繁的，基本每20分钟一趟。大家可以直接到台北车站现场购买，台北车站台铁有人工窗口售票和自助售票机。可以连返程票一起买了。</span></p>
<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240);"><strong style="word-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">3</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;">、7-11台铁订票</span></strong></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">想要购买台铁车票的朋友不用再特地到台铁车站了，只要到附近的7-11、全家、OK、莱尔富…等4家便利商店就可以直接买到对号列车的车票，不过，要付8元的手续费。</span></span></p>
