 background: white;">葛玛兰汽车客运官网：</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><a href="/fishtrip/taiwan/taibei/" style="word-wrap: break-word;" target="_blank">http://www.tan90.cn/fishtrip/taiwan/taibei/</a></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background: white;">首都客运官网：</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><a href="/fishtrip/taiwan/taibei/" style="word-wrap: break-word;" target="_blank">http://www.tan90.cn/fishtrip/taiwan/taibei/</a></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word;"><br><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">宜兰就像是</span><a href="/fishtrip/taiwan/taibei/" class="relatedlink" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; text-decoration: none !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" target="_blank">http://www.tan90.cn/fishtrip/taiwan/taibei/</a><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">的后花园，少了台北都市的繁华和喧嚣，多了田园乡村的宁静和柔美。到宜兰也可赏鲸、体验飞行伞、大啖海鲜！非常适合假期休闲游。住在当地人的民宿里，感受宁静与温情。</span></span></span></p>
